! [[Download manager|Download management]]
! Password managing&nbsp;{{refn|In many integrated password saving tools there are often leaks that make them unsafe.<ref name="eweek">{{cite web|url=http://www.eweek.com/c/a/Security/Google-Chrome-and-Apple-Safari-Lead-Poor-Showing-by-Browsers-in-Password-Management-Test/ |title=Test Finds Google Chrome, Apple Safari Weakest in Browser Password Management|last=Prince|first=Brian|date=15 December 2008|publisher=[[eweek]]|accessdate=22 May 2009}}</ref>|group=note|name=pwd}}
