|}

As new tests are added, bogus ones removed, etc., new versions of [https://html5test.com/ html5test.com] become available as preliminary [https://beta.html5test.com/ beta] or even [https://alpha.html5test.com/ alpha] versions. These are great to test development versions (e.g. nightly builds) of web browsers, but their results should be taken with a grain of salt. Especially when considering that some browsers have experimental features built in which may be switched off by default.

