==Protocol support==
Information about what [[internet protocol]]s the browsers support (in addition to [[Hypertext Transfer Protocol|HTTP]] that all (modern) browser should and do fully support<ref group="note" name="Mosaic"/>). External links lead to information about support in future versions of the browsers or extensions that provide such functionality.
