'''Sipa USA''' was established in 1987 as the US Bureau for the Paris-based Sipa Press, which was founded in 1973 by Turkish [[photojournalist]] [[Gökşin Sipahioğlu]].

Sipa is an international photo agency specializing in editorial news and entertainment content. Sipa distributes its content directly to leading domestic publications as well as a worldwide network of partners.

In January 2013, Hamburg-based [http://www.ddpimages.com ddp images] acquired Sipa USA, thereby strengthening its position in the realm of photojournalism.

